      "Epoch 06 | train loss 0.0326 acc 0.9942 | val loss 0.0605 acc 0.9824\n",
      "Epoch 07 | train loss 0.0274 acc 0.9952 | val loss 0.0290 acc 0.9935\n",
      "Epoch 08 | train loss 0.0242 acc 0.9952 | val loss 0.0168 acc 0.9971\n",
      "Epoch 09 | train loss 0.0200 acc 0.9965 | val loss 0.0132 acc 0.9988\n",
      "Epoch 10 | train loss 0.0174 acc 0.9969 | val loss 0.0156 acc 0.9959\n",
      "Epoch 11 | train loss 0.0142 acc 0.9969 | val loss 0.0160 acc 0.9971\n",
